COMMENT     The sequence is circular, however the sequence begins with a unique
            EcoRI site. Bases 426-706, 1153-1583 and 2918 to 3735 were
            determined while the rest of the sequence was taken from the
            published sequence of pSC101, Tn9 and p15A.
